<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>EMA512_02_SU_0005_s</title>

  <!-- 공통 js-->
  <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

  <!-- 공통 css-->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

  <!-- 개별 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_01.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema512_02.css" />

  <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema512_02_0005.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema512_02_su_0005" data-current-page="page_2">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="3_green" lang="y">8의 약수를 모두 구해 봅시다.</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="input_area">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">나눗셈식을 이용하여 8의 약수를 모두 구해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="page_1_cover">
            <div class="input_area">
              <div class="question_box">
                <div class="flex">
                  <span>8&divide;</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span>=8</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex">
                  <span>8&divide;</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span>=4</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_area">
              <div class="question_box">
                <div class="flex">
                  <span>8&divide;</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span>=2</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex">
                  <span>8&divide;</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span>=1</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">곱셈식을 이용하여 8의 약수를 모두 고르고, 알게 된 점을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="flex upper">
            <div class="example_number">
              <span>1&times;8=8</span>
              <span>2&times;4=8</span>
            </div>

            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="true">1</button>
              <button data-answer-single="true">2</button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">3</button>
              <button data-answer-single="true">4</button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">5</button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">6</button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">7</button>
              <button data-answer-single="true">8</button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">9</button>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="leftside input_area">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">곱이 8이 되는 곱셈식에서 곱하는 두 수는 8의 약수입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="btn_area">
        <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
        <button class="btnReset" lang="y">리셋</button>
        <button class="btnCheck" lang="y">확인</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>